#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
Phased Audit Tool

This tool performs a 5-phase security audit on network devices.
Phases:
1. Connectivity Verification
2. Authentication Testing
3. Configuration Audit
4. Risk Assessment
5. Reporting and Recommendations
"""

